<h2 id="node">Node</h2>

<p>The node concept can be instantiated as a device, service, or function to offer different granularity levels. The node concept is a network component and is linked with other nodes through relationships. Furthermore, a node has the capability to act as and trustor or trustee based on the role of the interaction.</p>

