<h2 id="trustor-and-trustee">Trustor and Trustee</h2>

<p>The trustor is a deliberate agent that aims to fulfill its objective by relying on the actions of another agent who appears to be willing and capable to support the trustor based on the agreed conditions in a given environment as illustreated in the figure below. 
The trustee is a capable and willing agent to produce outcomes based based on requested actions from trustors in a given environment as illustreated in the figure below.</p>

